--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
I: improvement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 1.0.3 (2018-12-12)
I: Update filters to support Ansible >= 2.9

* Version 1.0.2 (2018-12-12)
I: Minor Jinja2 style improvement

* Version 1.0.1 (2018-12-12)
B: Fix bug introduced with Jinja2 style improvements

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-12)
I: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'
I: Minor style improvement
I: Rename config parameters

* Version 0.3.1 (2018-05-31)
I: Correct 'command' variable names

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-05-21)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 0.2.1 (2018-04-24)
I: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-01-10)
I: Improve Jinja2 filters

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-01-05)
F: Initial release
